Text:
Thanks for this amanrulz.  It is full of stuff,  and plenty of tips.
It takes a little getting used to the layout,  and people shouldn't be put off by the first few pages.
It could use some polishing,  but since it is full of information,  I am more than willing to look past that.  
Thanks again.

Thanks for the Tips & Tricks. Love Photoshop.
Keep it up.
